<plot>Marina is a girl who saves a colt from being put down (euthanized) because of a trauma. Marina works as a horse groom, because nobody believes that she can be a good rider. Now she has a chance, and she gives him the name - Grand. She is a dedicated caretaker, and she is dreaming of raising Grand to become a champion. Nobody believes in Grand's future except Marina. She works on Grand's recovery and growth and after some time Grand receives a clear bill of health from the vet. Driven by her dream she becomes a horse-rider and practices with Grand everyday.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?143783</url></doc>
